    <h1>Log File Analysis</h1>
    <p class="description">The process of reviewing raw server access logs to see exactly what Googlebot crawls, which URLs it ignores, and where it wastes budget. The <strong>most complete picture of crawler behaviour</strong> available — more granular than anything in Google Search Console.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
